      "date": "2016-09-07 19:31:20.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTrevis Autotest started enforced review-dne-part-1 session. The following test requirements were specified: fortestonly=true alwaysuploadlogs=true trivial=true testlist=sanity,sanity,sanity,sanity,sanity,sanity,sanity,sanity",
