      "date": "2016-09-08 14:37:17.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest from trevis-3vm1 for custom received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/f3c1c070-75cf-11e6-8afd-5254006e85c2). Ran 10 tests. No failures.",
